{"tid":1494893,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（和理非）十月一全香港都中華民國國旗，大家點睇","createTime":"2019-08-21T23:29:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T18:53:05.000Z","uid":42884,"like":46,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"eda8533382b1384b37dffe742971f4aafaf000e5","tid":1494893,"uid":42884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:29:13.000Z","msg":"見有巴打話十一想燒黨旗，雖然係合法，同相信好多和理非都唔鐘意<br />\n<br />\n我自己諗到個啱曬和理非同大中華膠嘅方法<br />\n如果喺中共立國當日，全香港都青天白日滿地紅旗，一定激死佢<br />\n而且一定合法<br />\n仲可以話畀全世界中共立國70年都仲未能夠贏人心<br />\n同時相信可以喺台灣做到好多Noise<br />\n<br />\n而且中共就無得再話我地要分裂中國，因為真正分裂中國嘅喺共產黨<br />\n<br />\n首先，我地要正名十一為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中華民國大陸共產主義淪陷日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n喺十一到雙十期間，將全港貼滿青天白日滿地紅旗<br />\n回歸之前本身香港就好多地方會喺雙十掛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rE5BZmt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrE5BZmt.png&h=aa2ee7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就可以全民大合唱，中華民國國旗歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wPiPgvZjNtg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwPiPgvZjNtg&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn060EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=e246ee27\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wPiPgvZjNtg</a><br />\n<br />\n我呢掛睇左呢個YouTube channel，見到主持人不停以中華民國嚟惡搞大陸，其實香港人都可以諗下呢招<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vGV0EVjl2tc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvGV0EVjl2tc&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn060EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=fc238368\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vGV0EVjl2tc</a>"},{"pid":"ba393ad3a250295711578f1792b0ca78430f9122","tid":1494893,"uid":13690,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:33:43.000Z","msg":"臺灣自己都嘈緊係中華民國定係臺灣"},{"pid":"0ab6282e78c472ab9eccc5b4fee3ec9782b91735","tid":1494893,"uid":130140,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:37:16.000Z","msg":"好咩？<br />\n會唔會掛黑色抽氣扇旗應景啲？"},{"pid":"66e7b30799e6927afa1f88bcb609a8aec53f4f8a","tid":1494893,"uid":273256,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:43:16.000Z","msg":"你地究竟知唔知呢支旗代表嘅國民黨係親中集團，呢支旗對好多台灣人黎講係當年白色恐怖同威權嘅歷史，無一個台灣年輕人會肯拎呢支旗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8fc196c2c09e24d5124778ba980ba67b69210d","tid":1494893,"uid":42884,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0ab6282e78c472ab9eccc5b4fee3ec9782b91735","tid":1494893,"uid":130140,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:37:16.000Z","msg":"好咩？<br />\n會唔會掛黑色抽氣扇旗應景啲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:45:21.000Z","msg":"71放黑色抽氣扇係好，但十一最落到中共面嘅係佢70年前想推翻嘅國家嘅旗<br />\n仲要喺70年呢個國家都仲存在<br />\n<br />\n如果全香港都青天白日滿地紅旗，可以畀人一個訊息，<br />\n香港人就係唔服你共產黨<br />\n🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼"},{"pid":"167b5cc55d9e2bfe032b565ee1a863ce7c19c7cb","tid":1494893,"uid":38218,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:46:59.000Z","msg":"舉美國旗，唱美國歌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqhXJYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqhXJYA.jpg&h=7d73fb26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b8bca0a66d8f35b08f3b42539ac11986522877b","tid":1494893,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:50:08.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民國台灣高壓統治不亞於支那"},{"pid":"6c3996611314d3ae61bfc009cf5c32571dc9b9f6","tid":1494893,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"167b5cc55d9e2bfe032b565ee1a863ce7c19c7cb","tid":1494893,"uid":38218,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:46:59.000Z","msg":"舉美國旗，唱美國歌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqhXJYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqhXJYA.jpg&h=7d73fb26&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T23:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95425dfdbdf5